snippet: Fire officials say a deck collapsed during a house party in suburban Atlanta and about a dozen people were injured, including several people who were burned by a grill....

headline.print_headline: About a Dozen People Hurt When Deck Collapses
headline.main: About a Dozen People Hurt When Deck Collapses

lead_paragraph: Fire officials say a deck collapsed during a house party in suburban Atlanta and about a dozen people were injured, including several people who were burned by a grill.
